## How FillPrompt() Assembles the Payload

When the user hits Generate Draft, `FillPrompt()` replaces all placeholders:

```
{Role}      ← RoleInstruction
{Tone}      ← ToneDirectives[selected tone]
{Length}    ← LengthMap[selected length]
{Structure} ← Structure field
{Intent}    ← Intent field
{MainType}  ← MainType field
{SubType}   ← SubType field
{UserInput} ← what the user typed in the context box
```

The user never sees any of this. They see four dropdowns and a text box. The pack does the rest.

